fore the music starts. However, the sounds that are the products of the technology of the human body are extremely sharp and clear. A human ear never perceives a sound accompanied by a hissing sound or with atmospherics as does HI-FI; it perceives sound e
xactly as it is, sharp and clear. This is the way it has been since the creation of man.
